contents:
[package]
name = "accesskit"
version = "0.12.2"
authors = [ "The AccessKit contributors",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "UI accessibility infrastructure across platforms"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "accessibility",]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.68.2"

[features]
serde = [ "dep:serde", "enumn",]
schemars = [ "dep:schemars", "serde",]

[dependencies.enumn]
version = "0.1.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.pyo3]
version = "0.20"
optional = true

[dependencies.schemars]
version = "0.8.7"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "schemars", "serde",]

[package]
name = "accesskit_consumer"
version = "0.17.0"
authors = [ "The AccessKit contributors",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit consumer library (internal)"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "accessibility",]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.68.2"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.12.2"
path = "../common"

[package]
name = "accesskit_macos"
version = "0.11.0"
authors = [ "The AccessKit contributors",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: macOS adapter"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "accessibility",]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.68.2"

[dependencies]
objc2 = "0.5.0"
once_cell = "1.13.0"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.12.2"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.accesskit_consumer]
version = "0.17.0"
path = "../../consumer"

[dependencies.icrate]
version = "0.1.0"
features = [ "AppKit", "AppKit_NSAccessibilityElement", "AppKit_NSView", "AppKit_NSWindow", "Foundation", "Foundation_NSArray", "Foundation_NSMutableDictionary", "Foundation_NSNumber", "Foundation_NSThread",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
default-target = "x86_64-apple-darwin"

[package]
name = "accesskit_unix"
version = "0.7.1"
authors = [ "The AccessKit contributors",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: Linux adapter"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "accessibility",]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.68.2"

[features]
default = [ "async-io",]
async-io = [ "dep:async-channel", "dep:async-executor", "dep:async-task", "dep:futures-util", "atspi/async-std", "zbus/async-io",]
tokio = [ "dep:tokio", "dep:tokio-stream", "atspi/tokio", "zbus/tokio",]

[dependencies]
futures-lite = "1.13"
once_cell = "1.17.1"
serde = "1.0"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.12.2"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.accesskit_consumer]
version = "0.17.0"
path = "../../consumer"

[dependencies.atspi]
version = "0.19"
default-features = false

[dependencies.zbus]
version = "3.14"
default-features = false

[dependencies.async-channel]
version = "2.1.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-executor]
version = "1.5.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-task]
version = "4.3.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.27"
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
version = "0.1.14"
optional = true

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.32.0"
optional = true
features = [ "macros", "net", "rt", "sync", "time",]

[package]
name = "accesskit_windows"
version = "0.16.0"
authors = [ "The AccessKit contributors",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: Windows adapter"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "accessibility",]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.68.2"

[dependencies]
once_cell = "1.13.0"
paste = "1.0"
static_assertions = "1.1.0"

[dev-dependencies]
scopeguard = "1.1.0"

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.12.2"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.accesskit_consumer]
version = "0.17.0"
path = "../../consumer"

[dependencies.windows]
version = "0.48.0"
features = [ "implement", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_System_Com", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Ole", "Win32_UI_Accessibility", "Win32_UI_Input_KeyboardAndMouse", "Win32_UI_WindowsAndMessaging",]

[dev-dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/winit.git"
branch = "winit-0.29"

[package]
name = "accesskit_winit"
version = "0.18.1"
authors = [ "The AccessKit contributors",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "AccessKit UI accessibility infrastructure: winit adapter"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "accessibility", "winit",]
repository = "https://github.com/AccessKit/accesskit"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.68.2"

[features]
default = [ "accesskit_unix", "async-io", "rwh_06",]
rwh_05 = [ "winit/rwh_05", "dep:rwh_05",]
rwh_06 = [ "winit/rwh_06", "dep:rwh_06",]
async-io = [ "accesskit_unix/async-io",]
tokio = [ "accesskit_unix/tokio",]

[dependencies.accesskit]
version = "0.12.2"
path = "../../common"

[dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/winit.git"
branch = "winit-0.29"
default-features = false

[dependencies.rwh_05]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.5"
features = [ "std",]
optional = true

[dependencies.rwh_06]
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.6"
features = [ "std",]
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/winit.git"
branch = "winit-0.29"
default-features = false
features = [ "x11", "wayland", "wayland-dlopen", "wayland-csd-adwaita",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "winit/rwh_06", "winit/x11", "winit/wayland",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.accesskit_windows]
version = "0.16.0"
path = "../windows"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.accesskit_macos]
version = "0.11.0"
path = "../macos"

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"linux\", target_os = \"dragonfly\", target_os = \"freebsd\", target_os = \"openbsd\", target_os = \"netbsd\"))".dependencies.accesskit_unix]
version = "0.7.1"
path = "../unix"
optional = true
default-features = false

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"linux\", target_os = \"dragonfly\", target_os = \"freebsd\", target_os = \"openbsd\", target_os = \"netbsd\"))".dependencies.winit]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/winit.git"
branch = "winit-0.29"
default-features = false
features = [ "x11", "wayland",]

[package]
name = "atomicwrites"
version = "0.4.2"
authors = [ "Markus Unterwaditzer <markus-honeypot@unterwaditzer.net>",]
license = "MIT"
keywords = [ "filesystem", "posix",]
readme = "README.md"
description = "Atomic file-writes."
documentation = "https://docs.rs/crate/atomicwrites"
homepage = "https://github.com/untitaker/rust-atomicwrites"
repository = "https://github.com/untitaker/rust-atomicwrites"
exclude = [ "/.travis.yml", "/Makefile", "/appveyor.yml",]

[dependencies]
tempfile = "3.1"

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies.rustix]
version = "0.38.0"
features = [ "fs",]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.48.0"
features = [ "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Storage_FileSystem",]

[package]
name = "clipboard_macos"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "A library to obtain access to the macOS clipboard"
license = "Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/window_clipboard"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/clipboard_macos"
keywords = [ "clipboard", "macos",]

[dependencies]
objc = "0.2"
objc_id = "0.1"
objc-foundation = "0.1"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
default-target = "x86_64-apple-darwin"

[package]
name = "clipboard_wayland"
version = "0.2.2"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "A library to obtain access to the clipboard of a Wayland window"
license = "Apache-2.0"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/window_clipboard"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/clipboard_wayland"
keywords = [ "clipboard", "wayland",]

[dependencies.smithay-clipboard]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/smithay-clipboard"
tag = "pop-dnd-4"
features = [ "dnd",]

[dependencies.mime]
path = "../mime"

[dependencies.dnd]
path = "../dnd"

[package]
name = "clipboard_x11"
version = "0.4.2"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "A library to obtain access to the X11 clipboard"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/window_clipboard"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/clipboard_x11"
keywords = [ "clipboard", "x11",]

[dependencies]
x11rb = "0.13"
thiserror = "1.0"

[package]
name = "cosmic-config"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = [ "macro", "subscription",]
dbus = [ "dep:zbus", "cosmic-settings-daemon", "futures-util", "subscription",]
macro = [ "cosmic-config-derive",]
subscription = [ "iced_futures",]

[dependencies]
notify = "6.0.0"
ron = "0.8.0"
serde = "1.0.152"
once_cell = "1.19.0"
dirs = "5.0.1"

[dependencies.zbus]
version = "3.14.1"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.atomicwrites]
git = "https://github.com/jackpot51/rust-atomicwrites"

[dependencies.calloop]
version = "0.13.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.cosmic-config-derive]
path = "../cosmic-config-derive/"
optional = true

[dependencies.iced]
path = "../iced/"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.iced_futures]
path = "../iced/futures/"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.cosmic-settings-daemon]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/dbus-settings-bindings"
branch = "cosmic-settings-daemon"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies]
xdg = "2.1"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
known-folders = "1.1.0"

[package]
name = "cosmic-config-derive"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
syn = "1.0"
quote = "1.0"

[[bench]]
name = "layout"
harness = false

[package]
name = "cosmic-text"
description = "Pure Rust multi-line text handling"
version = "0.11.2"
authors = [ "Jeremy Soller <jeremy@system76.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/cosmic-text/latest/cosmic_text/"
repository = "https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-text"
rust-version = "1.65"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2.4.1"
libm = "0.2.8"
log = "0.4.20"
rangemap = "1.4.0"
self_cell = "1.0.1"
unicode-linebreak = "0.1.5"
unicode-script = "0.5.5"
unicode-segmentation = "1.10.1"

[features]
default = [ "std", "swash", "fontconfig",]
fontconfig = [ "fontdb/fontconfig", "std",]
no_std = [ "rustybuzz/libm", "hashbrown",]
shape-run-cache = []
std = [ "fontdb/memmap", "fontdb/std", "rustybuzz/std", "sys-locale", "ttf-parser/std", "unicode-bidi/std",]
vi = [ "modit", "syntect", "cosmic_undo_2",]
wasm-web = [ "sys-locale?/js",]
warn_on_missing_glyphs = []

[workspace]
members = [ "examples/*",]

[dev-dependencies]
tiny-skia = "0.11.2"

[dependencies.cosmic_undo_2]
version = "0.2.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.fontdb]
version = "0.16.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.hashbrown]
version = "0.14.1"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.modit]
version = "0.1.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.rustc-hash]
version = "1.1.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.rustybuzz]
version = "0.12.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "libm",]

[dependencies.swash]
version = "0.1.12"
optional = true

[dependencies.syntect]
version = "5.1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.sys-locale]
version = "0.3.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.ttf-parser]
version = "0.20.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.unicode-bidi]
version = "0.3.13"
default-features = false
features = [ "hardcoded-data",]

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.5.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "cargo_bench_support",]

[profile.test]
opt-level = 1

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "vi",]

[package]
name = "cosmic-theme"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = []
gtk4-output = []
no-default = []
theme-from-image = [ "kmeans_colors", "image",]

[dependencies]
almost = "0.2"
ron = "0.8"
lazy_static = "1.4.0"
dirs = "5.0.1"
thiserror = "1.0.5"

[dependencies.palette]
version = "0.7.3"
features = [ "serializing",]

[dependencies.kmeans_colors]
version = "0.5"
features = [ "palette_color",]
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.24.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.129"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.csscolorparser]
version = "0.6.2"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.cosmic-config]
path = "../cosmic-config/"
default-features = false
features = [ "subscription", "macro",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "test_all_features",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[package]
name = "d3d12"
version = "0.19.0"
authors = [ "gfx-rs developers",]
description = "Low level D3D12 API wrapper"
repository = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu/tree/trunk/d3d12"
keywords = [ "windows", "graphics",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/d3d12"
categories = [ "api-bindings", "graphics", "memory-management", "os::windows-apis",]
edition = "2018"

[features]
implicit-link = []

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
bitflags = "2"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
targets = [ "x86_64-pc-windows-msvc",]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.libloading]
version = ">=0.7,<0.9"
optional = true

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3"
features = [ "dxgi1_2", "dxgi1_3", "dxgi1_4", "dxgi1_5", "dxgi1_6", "dxgidebug", "d3d12", "d3d12sdklayers", "d3dcommon", "d3dcompiler", "dxgiformat", "synchapi", "winerror",]

[package]
name = "dnd"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "2.5.0"
raw-window-handle = "0.6"

[dependencies.mime]
path = "../mime"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\", target_os=\"ios\", target_os=\"redox\"))))".dependencies.smithay-clipboard]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/smithay-clipboard"
tag = "pop-dnd-4"
features = [ "dnd",]

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\", target_os=\"ios\", target_os=\"redox\"))))".dependencies.sctk]
package = "smithay-client-toolkit"
git = "https://github.com/Smithay/client-toolkit"
default-features = false
features = [ "calloop",]
rev = "3bed072"

[package]
name = "glyphon"
description = "Fast, simple 2D text rendering for wgpu"
version = "0.5.0"
edition = "2021"
homepage = "https://github.com/grovesNL/glyphon.git"
repository = "https://github.com/grovesNL/glyphon"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0 OR Zlib"

[dependencies]
etagere = "0.2.10"
lru = "0.12.1"

[dev-dependencies]
pollster = "0.3.0"

[dependencies.wgpu]
git = "https://github.com/gfx-rs/wgpu"
rev = "20fda69"

[dependencies.cosmic-text]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/cosmic-text.git"

[dev-dependencies.winit]
version = "0.29.10"
features = [ "rwh_05",]

[package]
name = "iced"
description = "A cross-platform GUI library inspired by Elm"
version = "0.12.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[features]
wgpu = [ "iced_renderer/wgpu", "iced_widget/wgpu",]
image = [ "iced_widget/image", "dep:image",]
svg = [ "iced_widget/svg",]
canvas = [ "iced_widget/canvas",]
qr_code = [ "iced_widget/qr_code",]
lazy = [ "iced_widget/lazy",]
debug = [ "iced_winit?/debug", "iced_sctk?/debug",]
tokio = [ "iced_futures/tokio",]
async-std = [ "iced_futures/async-std",]
smol = [ "iced_futures/smol",]
palette = [ "iced_core/palette",]
web-colors = [ "iced_renderer/web-colors",]
webgl = [ "iced_renderer/webgl",]
highlighter = [ "iced_highlighter",]
multi-window = [ "iced_winit?/multi-window",]
advanced = []
a11y = [ "iced_accessibility", "iced_core/a11y", "iced_widget/a11y", "iced_winit?/a11y", "iced_sctk?/a11y",]
winit = [ "iced_winit", "iced_accessibility?/accesskit_winit",]
wayland = [ "iced_sctk", "iced_widget/wayland", "iced_accessibility?/accesskit_unix", "iced_core/wayland",]
wayland-clipboard = [ "iced_sctk?/clipboard",]

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0"

[workspace]
members = [ "core", "futures", "graphics", "runtime", "renderer", "style", "tiny_skia", "wgpu", "widget", "winit", "examples/*", "accessibility", "sctk",]
exclude = [ "examples/integration",]

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[dependencies.iced_futures]
version = "0.12"
path = "futures"

[dependencies.iced_renderer]
version = "0.12"
path = "renderer"

[dependencies.iced_widget]
version = "0.12"
path = "widget"

[dependencies.iced_winit]
features = [ "application", "application",]
optional = true
version = "0.12"
path = "winit"

[dependencies.iced_sctk]
optional = true
version = "0.1"
path = "sctk"

[dependencies.iced_highlighter]
optional = true
version = "0.12"
path = "highlighter"

[dependencies.iced_accessibility]
optional = true
version = "0.1"
path = "accessibility"

[dependencies.window_clipboard]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/window_clipboard.git"
tag = "pop-dnd-6"

[dependencies.mime]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/window_clipboard.git"
tag = "pop-dnd-6"

[dependencies.dnd]
git = "https://github.com/pop-os/window_clipboard.git"
tag = "pop-dnd-6"

[dependencies.image]
optional = true
version = "0.24"

[workspace.package]
version = "0.12.0"
authors = [ "Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector@hecrj.dev>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/iced-rs/iced"
homepage = "https://iced.rs"
categories = [ "gui",]
keywords = [ "gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "widgets",]

[workspace.dependencies]
async-std = "1.0"
bitflags = "2.5"
futures = "0.3"
glam = "0.24"
guillotiere = "0.6"
half = "2.2"
image = "0.24"
kamadak-exif = "0.5"
kurbo = "0.9"
log = "0.4"
lyon = "1.0"
lyon_path = "1.0"
num-traits = "0.2"
once_cell = "1.0"
ouroboros = "0.17"
palette = "0.7"
raw-window-handle = "0.6"
resvg = "0.37"
rustc-hash = "1.0"
smol = "1.0"
smol_str = "0.2"
syntect = "5.1"
sysinfo = "0.28"
thiserror = "1.0"
tiny-skia = "0.11"
tokio = "1.0"
tracing = "0.1"
unicode-segmentation = "1.0"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4"
wasm-timer = "0.2"
web-sys = "0.3"
web-time = "0.2"
winapi = "0.3"

[profile.release-opt]
inherits = "release"
codegen-units = 1
debug = false
lto = true
incremental = false
opt-level = 3
overflow-checks = false
strip = "debuginfo"

[workspace.dependencies.iced]
version = "0.12"
path = "."

[workspace.dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.12"
path = "core"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_futures]
version = "0.12"
path = "futures"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_graphics]
version = "0.12"
path = "graphics"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_highlighter]
version = "0.12"
path = "highlighter"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_renderer]
version = "0.12"
path = "renderer"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_runtime]
version = "0.12"
path = "runtime"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_style]
version = "0.12"
path = "style"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_tiny_skia]
version = "0.12"
path = "tiny_skia"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_wgpu]
version = "0.12"
path = "wgpu"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_widget]
version = "0.12"
path = "widget"

[workspace.dependencies.iced_winit]
version = "0.12"
path = "winit"
